import re
def truncate(num):
    return re.sub(r'^(\d+\.\d{,2})\d*$',r'\1',str(num))
In [53]:
def classification_indexes(X,y):
    
    X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(X, y, test_size=0.5, random_state=42)
    
    Scores_by_classifier = []
    
    #Perceptron
    clf = Perceptron(tol=1e-3, random_state=0)
    clf.fit(X_train, y_train)
    Scores_by_classifier.append(['Perceptron',truncate(clf.score(X_test, y_test)*100)])

    #Logistic Regression
    clf = LogisticRegression(random_state=0).fit(X, y)
    clf.fit(X_train, y_train)
    Scores_by_classifier.append(['Logistic Regression',truncate(clf.score(X_test, y_test)*100)])

    # MLPClassifier
    clf = MLPClassifier(random_state=1, max_iter=300).fit(X_train, y_train)
    clf.predict_proba(X_test[:1])
    clf.predict(X_test[:5, :])
    Scores_by_classifier.append(['MLPClassifier',truncate(clf.score(X_test, y_test)*100)])

    #KNeighborsClassifier
    neigh = KNeighborsClassifier(n_neighbors=7)
    neigh.fit(X_train, y_train)
    neigh.score(X_test, y_test)
    Scores_by_classifier.append(['KNeighborsClassifier',truncate(neigh.score(X_test, y_test)*100)])

    #NearestCentroid
    clf = NearestCentroid()
    clf.fit(X_train, y_train)
    Scores_by_classifier.append(['NearestCentroid',truncate(clf.score(X_test, y_test)*100)])

    #SVM
    clf = make_pipeline(StandardScaler(), SVC(gamma='auto'))
    clf.fit(X_train, y_train)
    clf.score(X_test, y_test)
    Scores_by_classifier.append(['SVM',truncate(clf.score(X_test, y_test)*100)])
    
    #Kmeans
    kmeans = KMeans(7, random_state=0)
    labels_a = kmeans.fit(X_train).predict(X_test)
    km = kmeans.fit(X_train)
    km_predict = kmeans.predict(X_test)
    km.score(X_test)
    Scores_by_classifier.append(['Kmeans',km.score(X_test)])
    
    #GaussianMixture
    gmm = GaussianMixture(n_components=7, random_state=0).fit(X_train)
    labels_b = gmm.predict(X_test)
    gmm.score(X_test,y_test)
    Scores_by_classifier.append(['GaussianMixture',gmm.score(X_test,y_test)])

    return Scores_by_classifier

def clustering_mapping(projectedpca,projectedLinearDiscriminantAnalysis,projectedIsomap,projectedKernelPCA,projectedLocallyLinearEmbedding,projectedSpectralEmbedding,projectedTSNE):
    #projectedpca
    #Kmeans
    components_groups = 8
    kmeans = KMeans(components_groups, random_state=0)
    labels_a_projectedpca = kmeans.fit(projectedpca).predict(projectedpca)
    #GaussianMixture
    gmm = GaussianMixture(n_components=components_groups, random_state=0).fit(projectedpca)
    labels_b_projectedpca = gmm.predict(projectedpca)
    #projectedLinearDiscriminantAnalysis
    #Kmeans
    kmeans = KMeans(components_groups, random_state=0)
    labels_a_projectedLinearDiscriminantAnalysis = kmeans.fit(projectedLinearDiscriminantAnalysis).predict(projectedLinearDiscriminantAnalysis)
    #GaussianMixture
    gmm = GaussianMixture(n_components=7, random_state=0).fit(projectedLinearDiscriminantAnalysis)
    labels_b_projectedLinearDiscriminantAnalysis = gmm.predict(projectedLinearDiscriminantAnalysis)
    #projectedIsomap
    #Kmeans
    kmeans = KMeans(components_groups, random_state=0)
    labels_a_projectedIsomap = kmeans.fit(projectedIsomap).predict(projectedIsomap)
    #GaussianMixture
    gmm = GaussianMixture(n_components=components_groups, random_state=0).fit(projectedIsomap)
    labels_b_projectedIsomap = gmm.predict(projectedIsomap)
    #projectedKernelPCA
    #Kmeans
    kmeans = KMeans(components_groups, random_state=0)
    labels_a_projectedKernelPCA = kmeans.fit(projectedKernelPCA).predict(projectedKernelPCA)
    #GaussianMixture
    gmm = GaussianMixture(n_components=components_groups, random_state=0).fit(projectedKernelPCA)
    labels_b_projectedKernelPCA = gmm.predict(projectedKernelPCA)
    #projectedLocallyLinearEmbedding
    #Kmeans
    kmeans = KMeans(components_groups, random_state=0)
    labels_a_projectedLocallyLinearEmbedding = kmeans.fit(projectedLocallyLinearEmbedding).predict(projectedLocallyLinearEmbedding)
    #GaussianMixture
    gmm = GaussianMixture(n_components=components_groups, random_state=0).fit(projectedLocallyLinearEmbedding)
    labels_b_projectedLocallyLinearEmbedding = gmm.predict(projectedLocallyLinearEmbedding)
    #projectedSpectralEmbedding
    #Kmeans
    kmeans = KMeans(components_groups, random_state=0)
    labels_a_projectedSpectralEmbedding = kmeans.fit(projectedSpectralEmbedding).predict(projectedSpectralEmbedding)
    #GaussianMixture
    gmm = GaussianMixture(n_components=components_groups, random_state=0).fit(projectedSpectralEmbedding)
    labels_b_projectedSpectralEmbedding = gmm.predict(projectedSpectralEmbedding)
    #projectedTSNE
    #Kmeans
    kmeans = KMeans(components_groups, random_state=0)
    labels_a_projectedTSNE = kmeans.fit(projectedTSNE).predict(projectedTSNE)
    #GaussianMixture
    gmm = GaussianMixture(n_components=components_groups, random_state=0).fit(projectedTSNE)
    labels_b_projectedTSNE = gmm.predict(projectedTSNE)
    
    fig, axes = plt.subplots(7, 2,figsize=(10,30))
    axes[0, 0].set_title('PCA - Kmeans')
    axes[0, 0].scatter(projectedpca[:, 0], projectedpca[:, 1], c=labels_a_projectedpca, s=40, cmap='viridis');
    axes[0, 1].set_title('PCA - GaussianMixture')
    axes[0, 1].scatter(projectedpca[:, 0], projectedpca[:, 1], c=labels_b_projectedpca, s=40, cmap='viridis');
    axes[1, 0].set_title('LinearDiscriminantAnalysis - Kmeans')
    axes[1, 0].scatter(projectedLinearDiscriminantAnalysis[:, 0], projectedLinearDiscriminantAnalysis[:, 1], c=labels_a_projectedLinearDiscriminantAnalysis, s=40, cmap='viridis');
    axes[1, 1].set_title('LinearDiscriminantAnalysis - GaussianMixture')
    axes[1, 1].scatter(projectedLinearDiscriminantAnalysis[:, 0], projectedLinearDiscriminantAnalysis[:, 1], c=labels_b_projectedLinearDiscriminantAnalysis, s=40, cmap='viridis');
    axes[2, 0].set_title('Isomap - Kmeans')
    axes[2, 0].scatter(projectedIsomap[:, 0], projectedIsomap[:, 1], c=labels_a_projectedIsomap, s=40, cmap='viridis');
    axes[2, 1].set_title('Isomap - GaussianMixture')
